@startuml
title GoF Pattern : Memento + Observer

note as GoFLabel
  **<<Memento + Observer>>**
end note

class Document {
  + id: String
  + content: String
  + createMemento(): Memento
  + restore(Memento): void
  + attach(o: Observer): void
  + detach(o: Observer): void
  + notify(): void
}
class Memento {
  # state: String
  # save(): void
  # restore(): void
}
class Caretaker {
  + history: List<Memento>
  + addMemento(Memento): void
  + removeMemento(): void
}
interface Observer {
  - update(): void
}
class Toolbar {
}
class StatusBar {
}
class PreviewPanel {
}

Document --> Memento : history
Caretaker *--> Memento : history
Document --> Observer : observers
Toolbar ..> Document
StatusBar ..> Document
PreviewPanel ..> Document
GoFLabel .. Document
@enduml